paper_keywords: one-dimensional four-qubit cluster and cluster-class states
paper_abstract: We propose two protocols for remotely preparing a two-qubit entangled state, where the quantum channels take the form of one-dimensional four-qubit cluster and cluster-class states, respectively. The total success probability and classical communication cost are also calculated.
paper_title: REMOTE PREPARATION OF TWO-QUBIT ENTANGLED STATE VIA ONE-DIMENSIONAL FOUR-QUBIT CLUSTER AND CLUSTER-CLASS STATES
